label ppe_start
P.P.E Simulation!\
In this training, you’ll learn how to correctly wear personal protective equipment before entering the lab.
Your task will be to select and equip the correct safety gear — including your lab coat, gloves, and goggles.\
Each item must be worn in the correct order to ensure proper protection.
As part of this training, you’ll enforce lab safety standards.  That means disposing of waste properly, keeping food and drinks out, and following all protective procedures.
[signal arg="proceed"]
[end_timeline]
