label microscope_start
Microscope Handling Simulation!\
In this activity, you’ll learn about the parts, functions, and safe handling of a compound microscope.
You’ll begin with a guided walkthrough where you can click on each microscope part to explore its purpose and learn helpful tips.
Then, you’ll move on to an interactive practice session — where you’ll carry, set up, and focus the microscope just like in a real lab!
[signal arg="proceed"]
[end_timeline]
