label measurement_start
Measurement Simulation!\
In this activity, you’ll learn how to measure length, mass, and volume using virtual lab tools.
You’ll also  practice unit conversions, apply correct measuring techniques, and understand the difference between accuracy and precision.
you’ll explore how to take consistent measurements, avoid common mistakes, and improve your lab skills step by step.\
By the end, you’ll be able to record and convert data confidently just like a real lab technician!
[signal arg="proceed"]
[end_timeline]
